	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l491" cert="high">Argentina</placeName> 2. augusti: <persName type="auto_name">Comes Valdechius</persName> discessit a <persName type="citizen_name">Guysio</persName> ad <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8315">Condensem</persName> cum septingentis equitibus.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ringravius asserit se non pugnaturum contra suae religionis homines.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Fertur <persName type="auto_name">Guisius</persName> obsessurus <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l367" cert="high">Aureliam</placeName>, ubi <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8315">Condeus</persName> se continet.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">- Scribitur ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l15" cert="high">Antverpia</placeName> <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18554">reginam Angliae</persName> magnum instruere exercitum, quem mittat in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Galliam</placeName> in auxilium Condei.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Causa huius apparatus fertur, quod <persName type="auto_name">Guisius</persName> impegerit colaphum legato <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18554">reginae Angliae</persName>.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">- <persName type="auto_name">Andelotus</persName> hac transivit ad principes protestantes.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Creditur eum auxilia impetraturum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Interceptae sunt literae cardinalis <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l691" cert="high">Lotharingii</placeName> e <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l378" cert="high">Lutetia</placeName> ad <persName type="citizen_name">regen Navarrae</persName>, in quibus praeter multa alia archana continetur, quod post mensem ignoret, undenam pecuniae comparari possint ad sustinendum bellum...; quod <persName type="citizen_name">Navarrae regina</persName> veniret in auxilium <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8315">Condei</persName> cum sex millibus peditum.</s>
					<note type="misc">Bis hierher von andrer Hand, das Folgende von <persName ref="p495" type="auto_name">Bullinger</persName> geschrieben.</note> 
					<s n="9" xml:lang="de" type="manual">Wyter ist schryben har kummen, der herr von Anderes habe in <placeName type="citizen_name">Provincia</placeName> geschlagen die bäpstler und sy erlegt, doch sye houptman <persName type="citizen_name">Studer</persName> von <placeName ref="l473" cert="high">S. Gallen</placeName> mitt 14 siner knächten umbkummen...</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="de" type="manual">Die <placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Berner</placeName> zühind uff <placeName type="citizen_name">Schaloni</placeName><note type="misc"><persName ref="p495" type="auto_name">Bullinger</persName> glaubt beides nicht.</note>.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Es ist einer kummen von <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l378" cert="high">Parys</placeName>, sagt, die 15 fendli <persName type="citizen_name">Frölichs</persName> syend näben <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l378" cert="high">Parys</placeName> hin ins <placeName type="citizen_name">Gwysa</placeName> läger zogen, also 1200 schwartz rütter und [er] <placeName type="auto_name">Rogendorff</placeName>, 20 fenli lantzknächt under dem Ryngraffen, und achte man, <placeName type="citizen_name">Gwysa</placeName> werde schlahen wöllen oder <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l367" cert="high">Orliantz</placeName> belägern.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Ist's waar, so ist darzu das lang beyten guͦt.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Man hept an vil sagen von vil rüstung und tagens der <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2448" cert="high">5 Orten</placeName>, <placeName ref="l760" cert="high">Solenthurn</placeName> etc.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Gott gäb, dass ettwas guͦts gäbe.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Und wie kumpt's, das ir mir nüt schrybend vom concilio?</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Es sol doch in wäsen und definitionibus gar sin.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse fehlt.]</note>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
